<h2>Blog</h2>

<p>Blog posts are listed below. Check back regularly for updates on EMOM events, artist spotlights, and the Sydney electronic music scene.</p>

{% if collections.posts.length === 0 %}
  <p><em>No posts yet. Check back soon!</em></p>
{% else %}
  <div class="posts-list">
    {% for post in collections.posts %}
    <article class="post-preview">
      <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
      <p class="post-date">{{ post.date | dateFilter }}</p>
      <p class="post-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
      <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read more â†’</a>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
{% endif %}
